question:
Consider the following code snippet. What is the output if three threads (t1, t2, t3) are started? 

class Counter {
    int count = 0;
    public void increment() { count++; }
}

class MyThread extends Thread {
    Counter c;
    public void run() { c.increment(); }
}

// In main:
Counter sharedCounter = new Counter();
MyThread t1 = new MyThread(); t1.c = sharedCounter;
MyThread t2 = new MyThread(); t2.c = sharedCounter;
MyThread t3 = new MyThread(); t3.c = sharedCounter;
t1.start(); t2.start(); t3.start();
t1.join(); t2.join(); t3.join();
System.out.println(sharedCounter.count);
